Title: How to 3D print your own GitHub models
Description:
Did you know you can 3D print the models used in GitHub's branding right at home? In this tour of the Maker Space at GitHub Universe, we show you how we converted our digital assets into physical prints. Learn how we embed magnets for weight and handle overhangs with supports.

#3DPrinting #GitHub #GitHubUniverse
